    "content": {
      "rendered": "<h2><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong>Updated:</strong> </span><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2018/12/03/2019-cause-awareness-giving-day-calendar-for-nonprofits/\"><strong>2019 Cause Awareness &amp; Giving Day Calendar</strong></a></h2>\n<hr />\n<p>Cause awareness and giving days can be very powerful themes upon which to launch\u00a0online fundraising campaigns. The real-time, in-the-moment nature of cause awareness and giving days can inspire donors to give provided that\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2017/11/14/cause-awareness-giving-day-campaigns-for-nonprofits/\"><strong>your nonprofit knows how to promote the days effectively</strong></a>.<strong>\u00a0</strong>The\u00a0first step is to decide which days to build a campaign upon and add them to your 2018 editorial calendar. In addition to the days listed below, see also\u00a0<strong><a href=\"http://publicholidays.global/\">public holidays by country</a></strong>, <strong><a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/\">Days of the Year</a></strong>, and <strong><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_commemorative_months\">Wikipedia&#8217;s List of Commemorative Months</a>.</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>January</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>15: <a href=\"http://mlkday.gov/\">Martin Luther King, Jr. Day of Service</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23MLKDay&amp;src=typd\">#MLKDay</a><br />\n21: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Religion_Day\">World Religion Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldReligionDay\">#WorldReligionDay</a><br />\n</strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>February</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>2: <a href=\"https://www.ramsar.org/activity/world-wetlands-day-2018\">World Wetlands Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldWetlandsDay&amp;src=typd\">#WorldWetlandsDay</a><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Cancer_Day\"><br />\n</a>4: <a href=\"http://www.worldcancerday.org/\">World Cancer Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldCancerDay\">#WorldCancerDay<br />\n</a>13: <a href=\"http://www.diamundialradio.org/\">World Radio Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldRadioDay\">#WorldRadioDay</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldWhaleDay\"><br />\n</a>14: <a href=\"https://bonoboproject.org/save-the-bonobo/world-bonobo-day/\">World Bonobo Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldBonoboDay\">#World Bonobo Day</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldCancerDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>14: <a href=\"https://www.vday.org/homepage.html\">V-Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/VDay\">#VDay</a><br />\n18: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/world-whale-day/\">World Whale Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldWhaleDay\">#WorldWhaleDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.onebillionrising.org/\"><strong><br />\n</strong></a><strong>20:</strong> <strong><a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/socialjusticeday/\">World Day of Social Justice</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23SocialJusticeDay\">#SocialJusticeDay</a><br />\n</strong><strong>22:</strong> <strong><a href=\"http://www.digitallearningday.org/\">Digital Learning Day</a></strong><strong>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23DLDay\">#DLDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldSpayDay\"><strong><br />\n</strong></a><strong>27: <a href=\"https://polarbearsinternational.org/get-involved/international-polar-bear-day\">International Polar Bear Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23PolarBearDay\">#PolarBearDay<br />\n</a>27: <a href=\"http://www.worldspayday.org/\">World Spay Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldSpayDay\">#WorldSpayDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23SocialJusticeDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>28: <a href=\"http://www.rarediseaseday.org/\">Rare Disease Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23RareDiseaseDay\">#RareDiseaseDay</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>March</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>3: <a href=\"http://wildlifeday.org/\">World Wildlife Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldWildlifeDay\">#WorldWildlifeDay</a><br />\n8:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.worldkidneyday.org/\">World Kidney\u00a0Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0#<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23worldkidneyday\">WorldKidneyDay</a><br />\n8: <a href=\"https://www.internationalwomensday.com/\">International Women&#8217;s Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WomensDay\">#WomensDay</a></strong><br />\n<strong>21: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/racialdiscriminationday/\">International Day for the Elimination of Racial Discrimination</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EndRacism\">#EndRacism<br />\n</a>21: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/forestsday/\">International Day of Forests</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23ForestsDay\">#ForestsDay<br />\n</a>21: <a href=\"https://www.worlddownsyndromeday.org/\">World Down Syndrome Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WDSD18\">#WDSD18</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23ForestsDay\"><br />\n</a>21: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/poetryday/\">World Poetry Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldPoetryDay\">#WorldPoetryDay</a><br />\n22:\u00a0<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Water_Day\">World Water Day</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldWaterDay\">#WorldWaterDay</a></strong><a style=\"font-size: 13px;\" href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldWaterDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a><strong>24: <a href=\"http://www.stoptb.org/events/world_tb_day/\">World Tuberculosis Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldTBDay&amp;src=typd\">#WorldTBDay<br />\n</a>24: <a href=\"http://www.earthhour.org/\">Earth Hour</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EarthHour\">#EarthHour</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>April</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>2: <a href=\"https://www.awarenessdays.com/awareness-days-calendar/world-autism-awareness-day-2018/\">World Autism Awareness Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldAutismDay&amp;src=typd\">#WorldAustismDay<br />\n</a>7: <a href=\"https://www.awarenessdays.com/awareness-days-calendar/world-health-day-2018/\">World Health Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldHealthDay\">#WorldHealthDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldAutismDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a><strong>12: <a href=\"http://www.streetchildrenday.org/\">International Day for Street Children</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23StreetChildrenDay\"><strong>#StreetChildrenDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>14:</strong> <strong><a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/dolphin-day/\">World Dolphin Day</a></strong><strong> &#8212;</strong> <strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23DolphinDay\">#DolphinDay</a><br />\n</strong><strong>15: <a href=\"http://www.weirdholiday.com/world-art-day/\">World Art Day</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldArtDay\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#WorldArtDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23StreetChildrenDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>22: <a href=\"http://www.earthday.org/\">Earth Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EarthDay&amp;src=typd\"><strong>#EarthDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>23: <a href=\"http://www.unesco.org/new/en/wbcd\">World Book Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldBookDay\">#WorldBookDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EarthDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a><strong>25: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Malaria_Day\">World Malaria Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldMalariaDay\"><strong>#WorldMalariaDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>25: <a href=\"http://www.greenpeace.org/international/en/getinvolved/Celebrate-World-Penguin-Day-by-protecting-their-homes/\">World Penguin Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldPenguinDay\">#WorldPenguinDay<br />\n</a>30: <a href=\"http://jazzday.com/\">International Jazz Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23JazzDay\">#JazzDay</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>May</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>1: <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Workers'_Day\">International Workers&#8217; Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23LaborDay\">#LaborDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?f=realtime&amp;q=%23LabourDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>3: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/pressfreedomday/\">World Press Freedom Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldPressFreedomDay\">#WorldPressFreedomDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?f=realtime&amp;q=%23LabourDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>10:\u00a0<a href=\"http://worldlupusday.org/\">World Lupus Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldLupusDay\">#WorldLupusDay</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GiveLocal17\"><br />\n</a>12: <a href=\"http://www.worldmigratorybirdday.org/\">World Migratory Bird Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldMigratoryBirdDay\">#WorldMigratoryBirdDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldLupusDay\"><strong><br />\n</strong></a><strong>12: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/fair-trade-day/\">World Fair Trade Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23FairTradeDay\">#FairTradeDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23BikeToWorkDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>17: <a href=\"http://dayagainsthomophobia.org\">International Day Against Homophobia, Transphobia, and Biphobia</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IDAHOT\">#IDAHOT</a></strong><br />\n<strong>18: <a href=\"http://network.icom.museum/international-museum-day\">International Museum Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23museumday\">#MuseumDay<br />\n</a>18: <a href=\"http://www.endangered.org/campaigns/endangered-species-day/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Endangered Species Day</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EndangeredSpeciesDay\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#EndangeredSpeciesDay</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23museumday\"><br />\n</a>22: <a href=\"https://www.cbd.int/idb/\">International Day for Biological Diversity</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23BiologicalDiversityDay\">#BiologicalDiversityDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WorldTurtleDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>23: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/turtle-day/\">World Turtle Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldTurtleDay&amp;src=typd\"><strong>#WorldTurtleDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>31:\u00a0<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_No_Tobacco_Day\">World No Tobacco Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldNoTobaccoDay\">#WorldNoTobaccoDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldTurtleDay&amp;src=typd\"><br />\n</a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>June</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>5: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Environment_Day\">World Environment Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldEnvironmentDay\">#WorldEnvironmentDay</a><br />\n8: <a href=\"http://worldoceansday.org/\">World Oceans Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldOceansDay\">#WorldOceansDay<br />\n</a>12: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/childlabourday/\">World Day Against Child Labor</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WDACL\">#WDACL</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldOceansDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>14: <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Blood_Donor_Day\">World Blood Donor Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldBloodDonorDay\">#WorldBloodDonorDay</a></strong><br />\n<strong>20: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/refugeeday/\">World Refugee Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldRefugeeDay\">#WorldRefugeeDay<br />\n</a>21: <a href=\"http://idayofyoga.org/\">International Day of Yoga</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23YogaDay\">#YogaDay<br />\n</a>22: <a href=\"http://www.worldrainforestday.com\">World Rainforest Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/worldrainforestday\">#WorldRainforestDay</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23YogaDay\"><br />\n</a>23:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.gaypridecalendar.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gay Pride Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/pride2018\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#Pride2018</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>July</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>11: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/populationday/\">WorldPopulationDay</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldPopulationDay\"><strong>#WorldPopulationDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>18: <a href=\"http://www.mandeladay.com/\">Nelson Mandela International Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23MandelaDay\">#MandelaDay<br />\n</a>28:</strong> <strong><a href=\"http://worldhepatitisday.org/\">World Hepatitis Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldHepatitisDay\">#WorldHepatitisDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Tiger_Day\"><br />\n</a><strong>29: <a href=\"http://tigerday.panda.org\">GlobalTiger Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/globaltigerday\">#GlobalTigerDay</a><br />\n30: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/humantrafficking/resources.shtml\">World Day Against Trafficking in Persons</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldDayAgainstTrafficking\">#WorldDayAgainstTrafficking</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>August</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>8: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/international-cat-day/\">International Cat Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23CatDay\">#CatDay</a><br />\n9: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/indigenousday/\">International Day of the World&#8217;s Indigenous Peoples</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IndigenousDay\"><strong>#IndigenousDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>10: <a href=\"http://www.worldlionday.com/\" rel=\"noopener\">World Lion Day</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldLionDay\" rel=\"noopener\">#WorldLionDay</a><br />\n12: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/youthday/\">International Youth Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23youthday\">#YouthDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/indigenousday/\"><br />\n</a><strong>12: <a href=\"http://worldelephantday.org/\">World Elephant Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldElephantDay\"><strong>#WorldElephantDay</strong></a><strong><br />\n</strong><strong>17: <a href=\"https://nationaldaycalendar.com/days-2/national-nonprofit-day-august-17/\" rel=\"noopener\">National Nonprofit Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nationalnonprofitday\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#NationalNonprofitDay</a> (Internationally recognized)</strong><br />\n<strong>18: <a href=\"http://isaronline.org/programs/international-homeless-animals-day-ihad/\" rel=\"noopener\">International Homeless Animal Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ihad18\">#IHAD18</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IHAD\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><br />\n</a></strong><strong>19: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/humanitarianday/\">World Humanitarian Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldHumanitarianDay\">#WorldHumanitarianDay<br />\n</a>26: <a href=\"https://www.daysoftheyear.com/days/dog-day/\">International Dog Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23DogDay\">#DogDay</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldHumanitarianDay\"><br />\n</a>29: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/againstnucleartestsday/\">International Day Against Nuclear Tests</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23AgainstNuclearTestsDay\">#AgainstNuclearTestsDay</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>September</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>5: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/charityday/\">International Day of Charity</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23CharityDay\">#CharityDay</a><br />\n8: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Literacy_Day\">International Literacy Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23LiteracyDay\"><strong>#LiteracyDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>10:\u00a0<a href=\"http://wspd.org.au\">World Suicide Prevention Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/wspd18\"><strong>#WSPD18</strong></a><br />\n<strong>15: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/democracyday/\">International Day of Democracy</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23DemocracyDay\">#DemocracyDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.internationaldayofpeace.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>21: <a href=\"http://internationaldayofpeace.org/\">International Day of Peace</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23PeaceDay\">#PeaceDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.worldrhinoday.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>22: <a href=\"http://www.worldrhinoday.org/\">World Rhino Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldRhinoDay\"><strong>#WorldRhinoDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>23: <a href=\"http://worldriversday.com/\">World Rivers Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldRiversDay\">#WorldRiversDay<br />\n</a>27: <a href=\"http://wtd.unwto.org/\">World Tourism Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldTourismDay\">#WorldTourismDay</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>October</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>2: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/habitatday/\">World Habitat Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldHabitatDay\">#WorldHabitatDay</a><br />\n4: <a href=\"http://www.worldanimalday.org.uk/\">World Animal Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldAnimalDay\"><strong>#WorldAnimalDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>5: <a href=\"https://worldcpday.org/\">World Cerebral Palsy Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldCPDay\">#WorldCPDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldAnimalDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>5: <a href=\"https://www.timeanddate.com/holidays/un/world-teachers-day\">World Teachers Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldTeachersDay\">#WorldTeachersDay</a></strong><br />\n<strong>10: <a href=\"http://www.who.int/mental_health/world-mental-health-day/\">World Mental Health Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldMentalHealthDay\"><strong>#WorldMentalHealthDay</strong><br />\n</a><strong>11: <a href=\"http://dayofthegirl.org/\">International Day of the Girl</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23DayOfTheGirl\">#DayOfTheGirl</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23NCOD\"><br />\n</a><strong>12: <a href=\"http://www.worldarthritisday.org/\">World Arthritis Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldArthritisDay\"><strong>#WorldArthritisDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>15: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/ruralwomenday/\">International Day of Rural Women</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23RuralWomenDay\">#RuralWomenDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldArthritisDay\"><strong><br />\n</strong></a><strong>16: <a href=\"http://www.fao.org/world-food-day\">World Food Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldFoodDay\">#WorldFoodDay<br />\n</a>16: <a href=\"https://globalcatday.org\" rel=\"noopener\">Global Cat Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/globalcatday\" rel=\"noopener\">#GlobalCatDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldArthritisDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>17: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/povertyday/\">International Day for the Eradication of Poverty</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EndPovertyDay\">#EndPoveryDay<br />\n</a>29: <a href=\"http://www.theinternetday.com/\">World Internet Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldInternetDay\">#WorldInternetDay<br />\n</a>31: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/citiesday/\">World Cities Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldCitiesDay\">#WorldCitiesDay</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>November</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>13: <a href=\"https://www.randomactsofkindness.org/world-kindness-day\">World Kindness Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldKindnessDay\">#WorldKindnessDay</a><br />\n14: <a href=\"https://www.awarenessdays.com/awareness-days-calendar/world-diabetes-day-2018/\">World Diabetes Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldDiabetesDay\"><strong>#WorldDiabetesDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>15: </strong><strong><a href=\"https://www.timeanddate.com/holidays/un/world-philosophy-day\">World Philosophy Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/worldphilosophyday\">#WorldPhilosophyDay</a><br />\n15: <a href=\"http://www.worldpancreaticcancerday.org/\">World Pancreatic Cancer Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WPCD\">#WPCD</a></strong><br />\n<strong>16: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/toleranceday/\">International Day for Tolerance</a> &#8212; </strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23ToleranceDay\"><strong>#ToleranceDay</strong></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23ToleranceDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>19: <a href=\"http://worldtoilet.org/\">World Toilet Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23worldtoiletday\">#WorldToiletDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldDiabetesDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>20: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/childrenday/\">Universal Children&#8217;s Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23ChildrensDay\"><strong>#ChildrensDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>21: <a href=\"http://www.worldtelevisionday.tv/\">World Television Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldTVDay\">#WorldTVDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23ChildrensDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>25: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/endviolenceday/\">International Day for the Elimination of Violence Against Women</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EndViolenceAgainstWomen\">#EndViolenceAgainstWomen<br />\n</a>27: <a href=\"http://givingtuesday.org\">Giving Tuesday</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23GivingTuesday\">#GivingTuesday</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EndViolenceAgainstWomen\"><br />\n</a></strong></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>December</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>1: <a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\">World AIDS Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldAIDSDay&amp;src=typd\">#WorldAIDSDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>3: <a href=\"http://www.idpwd.com.au/\">International Day of People with Disabilities</a>\u00a0&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IDPwD\">#IDPwD</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IDPWD\"><br />\n</a><strong>5: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/volunteerday/\">International Volunteer Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23VolunteerDay\">#VolunteerDay<br />\n</a>5: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/soilday/\">World Soil Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WorldSoilDay\">#WorldSoilDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IVD2014\"><br />\n</a><strong>9: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/anticorruptionday/\">International Anti-Corruption Day </a>&#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23AntiCorruptionDay\">#AntiCorruptionDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>10: <a href=\"http://www.ohchr.org/EN/AboutUs/Pages/HumanRightsDay.aspx\">International Human Rights Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23HumanRightsDay\">#HumanRightsDay</a></strong><br />\n<strong>11: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/mountainday/\">International Mountain Day</a>\u00a0&#8212;\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23mountainday\">#MountainDay<br />\n</a>18: <a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/migrantsday/\">International Migrants Day</a> &#8212; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23MigrantsDay\">#MigrantsDay</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">2018 Global Trends in Giving Report</h1>\n<p>Based upon the survey results of 6,057 donors worldwide, the <a href=\"http://givingreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>2018 Global Trends in Giving Report</strong></a>\u00a0summarizes donor data across six continents about how online and mobile technology effects giving. The report also examines the impact of gender, generation, ideology, religion, and donor size upon giving and volunteerism.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://givingreport.ngo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-22613 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Report-Blue-English-Twitter-600.jpg?resize=600%2C315\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Report-Blue-English-Twitter-600.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Report-Blue-English-Twitter-600.jpg?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n",
